      "content": "everything is gone. the fund, the company, all of it. i lost everything in the crash and the debt is just... it's impossible. i can't even think about going back home. the shame of looking my parents in the eye and telling them i blew their life savings is more than i can handle. i feel like i've already died, i'm just waiting for the rest of me to catch up.",
